The paper also investigates the robustness and expressiveness of the topological descriptors, which suggests that it may belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category, which deals with the development and analysis of machine learning algorithms. 

The paper involves the classification of different surface textures, which suggests that it may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category, which deals with the development of intelligent systems.
